paragraphs.body: Binkley grew up in Topeka, Kansas, and graduated from Washburn Rural High School.
paragraphs.text: Binkley grew up in Topeka, Kansas, and graduated from Washburn Rural High School.

paragraphs.body: Binkley is best known for his roles as Kenny James on the NBC sitcom My Name Is Earl and as Dan, the Del Taco spokesperson. He has also had guest spots on Gilmore Girls, Malcolm in the Middle, Sabrina, the Teenage Witch, Yes, Dear, The Drew Carey Show, Full House, and Wizards of Waverly Place.

paragraphs.body: Binkley once held a job making celebrity impersonation phone calls, posing as Don Knotts character Barney Fife. Binkley also did this impersonation in Behind the Camera: The Unauthorized Story of Three's Company.
